title: Read Optics Half Frame Reading Glasses | Comfortable, Stylish & Ready-to-Wear | Semi Rimless Reading Glasses, Mens Reading Glasses, Sun Reading Glasses for Women & Men | Black Sun Lens +1.5
features: OPTICAL PRECISION - The Read Optics semi-rimless glasses are created to offer unrivaled optical precision. Thoughtfully designed with spring hinges, adjustable rubber nose pads, and a lightweight & durable frame, they provide a comfortable fit for extended periods of use.

HALF-FRAMED & READY-TO-WEAR - Our glasses provide a timeless angular design, with a slim gunmetal half-frame and strong, flexible arms. Designed in a classic shape for a stylish & versatile look, each pair comes with a high-quality microfibre bag for safe storage & easy cleaning. Lens width: 50mm, bridge width: 19mm, arm length: 135mm, weight 25.6g.

SUN LENSES - The Read Optics sun reading glasses are specifically designed to protect your eyes from harmful UV rays, reduce glare & enhance your reading experience. Our lenses are anti-scratch, anti-smudge, and impact resistant & available in lens power + 0, 1.5, 2.0, 2.5, 3.0 & 3.5.

EXPLORE THE RANGE - Read Optics provide quality ready-to-wear reading glasses at affordable prices. We have a wide range of readers, that include classic, stylish and fashionable glasses for everyday wear. Please visit our storefront to explore the range.

THE READ OPTICS PROMISE - With a UK-based customer support team & over 30 years of industry experience, we are always here to assist you. Please get in touch in the unlikely event of any issues and we’ll do everything we can to put it right!
description: Read Optics - Designing & Manufactuing Ready to Wear Eyewear: We provide quality, ready to wear reading glasses at affordable prices, offering a wide range of non prescription eyewear. This includes our premium quality half frame metal sun reading glasses, ready to wear smoke tinted glasses so you can read safely in the sun whilst protecting your eyes. These sun readers for men have spring hinges and rubber nose pads for a comfortable adjustable fit. All our reading glasses come in multiple lens strengths and are designed to be lightweight and comfortable.
